OL,3,CSouthport killer's father 'failed to
OL,4,Ctell police about his fears over knife'
OL,6,FThe Southport Inquiry has heard the
OL,7,Fkiller's father failed to report the
OL,8,Ffact his son tried to take a taxi to
OL,9,Fhis former school with a suspected
OL,10,Fknife a week before last summer's
OL,11,Fattack.
OL,13,FAR as he is known in the inquiry had
OL,14,Fordered the taxi to The Range High
OL,15,FSchool in Formby, only for his father
OL,16,Fto "plead" with the driver "don't take
OL,17,Fhim".
OL,19,FThe dad later admitted he believed his
OL,20,Fson had a weapon in his backpack at
OL,21,Fthe time, but didn't raise the alarm.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
