OL,3,CSouthport killer's father 'failed to
OL,4,Ctell police about his fears over knife'
OL,6,FThe inquiry heard AR's father recalled
OL,7,Fhis son asking him when The Range High
OL,8,FSchool was breaking up for the summer.
OL,10,FHe had looked at his phone and told
OL,11,Fhim it was actually that day. He had
OL,12,Fthen said something along the lines of
OL,13,F"They'll all be going off to
OL,14,Funiversity now won't they?"
OL,16,FAnd AR is said to have replied: "Well
OL,17,FI won't be, will I?"
