OL,3,CSouthport killer's father 'failed to
OL,4,Ctell police about his fears over knife'
OL,6,FThe teenager had been expelled from
OL,7,Fthat school for carrying a knife and
OL,8,Fattacking a pupil with a hockey stick
OL,9,Ffive years earlier.
OL,11,FLater that day AR had called a taxi to
OL,12,Ftake him to the school but just as the
OL,13,Fdriver was about to leave- as was
OL,14,Fcaptured on this doorbell footage- his
OL,15,Ffather ran out of the house and
OL,16,Fpleaded with the driver not to take
OL,17,Fhim.
OL,19,FIn response AR had said "I'm 18. Take
OL,20,Fme."
