OL,4,Ctell police about his fears over knife'
OL,6,FBut the inquiry heard the driver
OL,7,Fdidn't want to be in the middle of a
OL,8,Fdomestic and left him there.
OL,10,FDCI Jason Pye confirmed AR's father
OL,11,Ftold police after the Southport attack
OL,12,Fhe suspected his son had been carrying
OL,13,Fa knife when he tried to go to the
OL,14,FSchool a week earlier.
OL,16,FBut he didn't report that incident to
OL,17,Fthe police.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
