OL,3,CSouthport killer's father 'failed to
OL,4,Ctell police about his fears over knife'
OL,6,FThe inquiry previously heard how AR
OL,7,Fhad used stolen IDs to order machetes
OL,8,Fonline and how he'd been building an
OL,9,Farsenal of weapons in his bedroom for
OL,10,Fat least two years.
OL,12,FHis father had told police on one
OL,13,Foccasion he'd signed for one of the
OL,14,Fmachetes his son had ordered and "hid
OL,15,Fit on top of a wardrobe".
OL,17,FThey also knew he had taken knives
OL,18,Ffrom the family home and had gone to
OL,19,Fschool with them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
