OL,6,FBut the DCI said nothing had been
OL,7,Ffound to suggest the parents
OL,8,F"sympathised with violent attacks or
OL,9,Fhad that mindset".
OL,11,FEarlier, Detective Chief Inspector
OL,12,FJason Pye told the hearing that a
OL,13,Fdedicated team of 80 officers were
OL,14,Fassigned to work for him, 37 of them
OL,15,Fassigned to supporting families of
OL,16,Fthose affected.
OL,18,FMerseyside Police received mutual aid
OL,19,Fsupport from neighbouring forces, he
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
