OL,6,FPye said the inquiry team spoke to 547
OL,7,Fwitnesses, compiled 1,244 exhibits,
OL,8,Fand read through 159,000 messages, the
OL,9,Fmajority of which were in Rwandan.
OL,11,FSir Adrian Fulford, the inquiry
OL,12,Fchairman, told the Inspector: "It
OL,13,Ftends to be forgotten that these
OL,14,Fevents can take a toll even on
OL,15,Fexperienced investigating officers.
OL,17,F"You have needed to liaise with a
OL,18,Fsignificant number of extremely
OL,19,Fdistressed individuals, and to
OL,20,Funderstand the fine detail of these
OL,21,Fextremely disturbing events.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
