OL,6,F"This included the need to gain a real
OL,7,Funderstanding of the precise sequence
OL,8,Fof events by viewing over and over
OL,9,Fagain some truly upsetting CCTV.
OL,11,F"You had to delve, as you've told us
OL,12,Fthis morning, insofar as one is able,
OL,13,Finto AR's depraved motivation and the
OL,14,Fhorrors that he was researching on the
OL,15,Finternet.
