OL,6,F"There is not the slightest suggestion
OL,7,Fthat you did all of that to anything
OL,8,Fless than the highest professional
OL,9,Fstandards and you have my thanks on
OL,10,Fbehalf of the public for your highly
OL,11,Feffective contribution, and those of
OL,12,Fyour brother and sister officers, into
OL,13,Fthe criminal investigation and into
OL,14,Fthis inquiry."
